document_data.name: Nanthleene
document_data.mainbody: '''Nanthleene''' was an inhabitant of [[Myth Drannor]] in the 3{{rd}} century [[DR]].
document_data.History: On {{yearlink|241}}, Nanthleene was at the [[Alastrarra]] manor when [[Elminster Aumar]] first came to [[Myth Drannor]].{{cite book/Elminster in Myth Drannor||4}} After they decided to let him go and have the [[Coronal]] judge him, per the head of the house, Nanthee gawked at the human a little too much.
